    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Presentable, practical, and priced to sell, this fair-condition car is a solid option for someone looking for dependable everyday transportation without spending a fortune. It shows the normal cosmetic wear and age you\u2019d expect, but overall it comes across as a usable, honest vehicle with plenty of life left for its next owner. A great fit for a commuter, first car, or budget-minded buyer who wants value and versatility.",
