    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking straightforward transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it offers solid value for a buyer who appreciates an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner. A smart opportunity for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project you can make your own.",
