      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly ride that could make a great project, backup car, or simple A-to-B commuter. If you appreciate a straightforward deal and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, there\u2019s real value here. Priced to be accessible and ready for someone who sees the opportunity.",
